{"tid":1477989,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鍵盤戰士開工喇！反對中文刪聆聽說話卷！","createTime":"2019-08-16T10:17:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T02:11:11.000Z","uid":153583,"like":43,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"0cfd5747a262b2688ec7ad6e78011205a51c7049","tid":1477989,"uid":153583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T10:17:16.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">9月16日截止喇! </span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">快啲send email反對呀!</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n教育局發佈諮詢文件嘅網頁: <a href=\"https://www.edb.gov.hk/tc/about-edb/press/consultation/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.edb.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fabout-edb%2Fpress%2Fconsultation%2F&d=bx%2Fd%2Fc%2BwyKmxZhRK7gjal0V6NNh9RYlaag4wFuTDRgw%3D&h=62848c1d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.edb.gov.hk/tc/about-edb/press/consultation/</a><br />\n是次諮詢文件直接連結: <a href=\"https://www.edb.gov.hk/attachment/tc/about-edb/press/consultation/TF_CurriculumReview_Consultation_c.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.edb.gov.hk%2Fattachment%2Ftc%2Fabout-edb%2Fpress%2Fconsultation%2FTF_CurriculumReview_Consultation_c.pdf&d=bx%2Fd%2Fc%2BwyKmxZhRK7gjal0V6NNh9RYlaag4wFuTDRgw%3D&h=0b5a028f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.edb.gov.hk/attachment/tc/about-edb/press/consultation/TF_CurriculumReview_Consultation_c.pdf</a><br />\n新聞報導: <a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/社區專題/354111/中文課程改革1-dse中文刪聆聽-說話-前線老師批-行回頭路\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%A4%BE%E5%8D%80%E5%B0%88%E9%A1%8C%2F354111%2F%E4%B8%AD%E6%96%87%E8%AA%B2%E7%A8%8B%E6%94%B9%E9%9D%A91-dse%E4%B8%AD%E6%96%87%E5%88%AA%E8%81%86%E8%81%BD-%E8%AA%AA%E8%A9%B1-%E5%89%8D%E7%B7%9A%E8%80%81%E5%B8%AB%E6%89%B9-%E8%A1%8C%E5%9B%9E%E9%A0%AD%E8%B7%AF&d=bx%2Fd%2Fc%2BwyKmxZhRK7gjal0V6NNh9RYlaag4wFuTDRgw%3D&h=0e27881f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/社區專題/354111/中文課程改革1-dse中文刪聆聽-說話-前線老師批-行回頭路</a><br />\n<br />\n我知大家都懶得睇晒全份諮詢文件架喇，所以節錄咗以下部分大家最關心嘅內容:<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">「中國語文和英國語文科有需要減少考試卷數及／或簡化校本評核以配合學生需要..... 至於中國語文科，可以探索公開考試的聆聽和／或說話部分，以及校本評核的實施是否可以修訂或減少以創造空間。」\n</code></pre><br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">「請於二零一九年九月十六日（星期一）或之前，以郵寄、電郵或傳真方式把書面意見交予專責小組秘書處：\n郵寄地址： 香港灣仔\n皇后大道東 213 號\n胡忠大廈 13 樓 1301 室\n學校課程檢討專責小組秘書處\n電郵： taskforce_cur@edb.gov.hk\n傳真號碼： (852) 2573 5299」</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">以下係我嘅範例email (建議大家唔好照抄，有時間就改改佢啦)</span></span><br />\n<br />\n學校課程檢討專責小組諮詢文件 - 反對中國語文科刪減聆聽及說話卷<br />\n<br />\n敬啟者:<br />\n<br />\n本人閱畢學校課程檢討專責小組諮詢文件，現特意來函反對中學文憑試中國語文科刪減聆聽及說話卷的建議。<br />\n<br />\n報告認為中文為本港大部分學生的母語，故此質疑聆聽及說話卷的價值。以此論調，既然中文為大部分學生的母語，學生聽說讀寫的能力應該皆為上品，中國語文科根本不用考核，整科理應可刪去。事實上，聆聽及說話的能力當中更包含表達及理解能力，並不單單是母語與否的問題，從考評局的報告亦可見每年考生於聆聽及說話卷當中的表現參差，數據上已說明報告的說法並不合理。<br />\n<br />\n觀乎政府高官均以中文為母語，然則無法聆聽市民訴求，又於記者會上屢屢答非所問、內容貧乏、邏輯混亂，可見以中文為母語並不代表聆聽及說話能力必定理想。<br />\n<br />\n聆聽及說話均為重要能力，對學生升學及投身職場有絕大幫助。強於讀寫的學生不一定強於言語上的溝通，反之亦然。<br />\n<br />\n本人謹此強調，聽說讀寫，四大能力，缺一不可。<br />\n<br />\n  此致<br />\n學校課程檢討專責小組秘書處<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\">市民<br />\n李老尾</div><br />\n<br />\n--------------------------------------------<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">大家可以起我底，我2月中曾經呼籲過大家喺咨詢期內反送中，不過冇乜人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 希望今次多啲人理我啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"9d684a887ac59b824e375ced7b7b235654011c76","tid":1477989,"uid":137309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T10:17:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"63e2aed55306fa3a52fd3411f28ddbb263a1ccbb","tid":1477989,"uid":153583,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T10:18:46.000Z","msg":"send email ---&gt; taskforce_cur@edb.gov.hk<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"857c62d8f43cdde647b798d870145cac505236e9","tid":1477989,"uid":241244,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T10:19:15.000Z","msg":"普教中！！！救下香港嘅下一代！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1475548\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1475548</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3d5b6f03d717d9ee2eaac4acd89dfdbbff5291fd","tid":1477989,"uid":153583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T10:20:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f6cd66394a9e6666bced446abc4347d2b2fd521","tid":1477989,"uid":153583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T10:22:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2de5a4736d483d833854c63e31559dceee2dd48b","tid":1477989,"uid":153583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T10:22:28.000Z","msg":"自推十連"},{"pid":"c48a7fbcce2d5416358e31ab991c5f982d02293f","tid":1477989,"uid":137309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T10:22:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1468af33a6afbb7b739bcccb7c532261339c3e4